PrecisAppointment of JOHN THOMAS McLENNAN, of Mahone Bay, Nova Scotia, as Chairman of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis, for a term of three years, or until the dissolution of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, whichever occurs first.
